description:
Kevin Clark, Nora Princiotti, and Danny Heifetz react to the Dak Prescott contract saga ending to the tune of four years and $160 million. They discuss some of the contract's intricacies, how it might affect future franchise QB contracts, and more.

Hosts: Kevin Clark, Nora Princiotti, and Danny Heifetz
